quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  9,25,DI granted VI victory many SITUACI. Tag Hunayn vi igx tro fier da your great numer. Consequently gxi ne help vi je all spacious ter igx straitened vi vi torn around fled
  9,26,Tiam DI send contentment His messenger believers. Li send down invisible soldat; Li tiel pun those disbelieved This est requital disbelievers
  9,27,Ultimately DI redeems whomever Li vol. DI est Forgiver Merciful
  9,28,O vi kred idol worshipers polluted ili ne permes approach Sankt Masjid post this jar! Se vi tim loss rent DI testament dusx vi kun His provisions en accordance kun His vol. DI est Omniscient SAGX
  9,29,Vi batal dors kontraux those ne kred en DI nor Last Tag nor do ili prohibit ki DI His messenger prohibited nor do ili abide per religi truth! - among those ricev scripture - gxis ili pag due impost volont unwillingly